[Match Selection Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=Some match selections may freeze or cause undesirable effects when combined with other match types. There are some unselectable match types that work. The values that have "??" I'm not sure what match type these are. If more characters are selected than a normal match type, then those selected characters will be in the match. The best values to use are "24" & "3B". Values "10" to "13" activate a Royal Rumble that causes The Rock to always come out after the countdown. Values "65", "66", "69", & "6A" are a type of Special Referee Two Referee match for Triple Threat & Fatal 4 Way matches both normal & Hell in a Cell. However, the characters that are designated as referees don't act like referees.
Values -
00 - Single No Manager
01 - Single No Manager Vs. W/ Manager
02 - Single No Manager Vs. W/ Two Managers
03 - Single W/ Manager Vs. W/ Manager
04 - Single W/ Manager Vs. W/ Two Managers
05 - Single W/ Two Managers Vs. W/ Two Managers
