[Player 1 Entrance Champion Label Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=This has your character labeled as whichever championship you wish to have. This is only cosmetic as it only affects the entrance label as you are making your way to the ring. Your character won't actually appear with the belt.
Values - 
00 - None
01 - WWF Champion
02 - Intercontinental Champion
03 - Hardcore Champion
04 - European Champion
05 - Light Heavyweight Champion
06 - Women's Champion
