[Player 1 is in 1st Person Mode]
author=BigBossman
description=This is probably best used in match that starts backstage with the arrows that allow you to go from area to area. Its only good for allowing you to explore the arena & other places. In order for this code to work, Players 2 - 8 must be either absent or eliminated. If its used when there is an active opponent, it will freeze.
patch=1,EE,006C4BFC,extended,00000001

[Player 1 Maximum Number of Finishers Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=It is possible for you to store more than 5 finishers. Again, the game won't display more than 5, but will allow you to build up more finishers, beyond 5.
