[Starting Location Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=If you fight in an area other than an arena (with a ring), you'll want to make sure that pinfalls count anywhere or have the Last Man Standing Rules on. If you select the match "Falls Count Anywhere" or "Hardcore", you'll still be able to move from one area to the next. This just determines where you start out at.
Values - 
0000 - Smackdown Arena
0001 - Raw is War Arena
0002 - Wrestlemania X7 Arena
0003 - Lobby
0004 - Plaza
0005 - Parking Lot
0006 - Boiler Room
0007 - WWF New York
0008 - VIP Room
0009 - Corridor A
000A - Corridor B
000B - Dressing Room A
000C - APA Office
000D - Storage Area
000E - Sunday Night Heat in a Smackdown Arena
000F - PPV Arena
0010 - Sunday Night Heat Arena
0011 - Commissioner's Office
0012 - Dressing Room B
0013 - Times Square
0014 - Smackdown B Arena (with the Fist)
patch=1,EE,10725BDA,extended,00000000

